    "body": "`spack load` didn't use the `prefix_inspections` from modules.yaml at all. All the other module systems use this mechanism to allow the user to configure those inspections.\r\n\r\nLet's take the prefix_inspections from modules.yaml configuration. If that is not available fall back to the old behaviour.",
